    <section ids="manage-flavors" names="manage\ flavors">
        <title>Manage flavors</title>
        <paragraph>In OpenStack, a flavor defines the compute, memory, and storage
            capacity of a virtual server, also known as an instance. As an
            administrative user, you can create, edit, and delete flavors.</paragraph>
